[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67087103]-咬我[/uid] (2026-05-07 14:57):[/b]<br/><br/>作为一个曾经从业过这个行业的人看到金螳螂爆拉我都惊呆了，对他得印象还停留在苏大的建筑公司[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>他还有洁净室概念  没想到吧<br/>我也没想到", "lou": 2421, "content_length": 39, "reply_to": 867217822, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778137131}, {"pid": 867219799, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 27, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-07 15:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867219235,45974302,4734]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67185238]我要把车坐塌[/uid] (2026-05-07 15:08):[/b]<br/><br/>我在sai佬问洁净室的那个帖子里看到有人提过，当时加自选了，当时好像好久都没启动，再看的时候已经开始板了。。[/quote]<br/>反正没有基本面 看他们玩就行了 我不喜欢这种纯吹的", "lou": 2422, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 867219235, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778137951}, {"pid": 867223279, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 322, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-07 15:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867220017,45974302,4735]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42162697]包子music[/uid] (2026-05-07 15:13):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，心情好的话能说说[b]常规月，跑赢大盘多少点算及格线吗[/b][s:ac:羡慕]打算给自己定个目标，用来回测逻辑的时候评价自己的操作[s:ac:怕]<br/><br/>3、4月的超跌和补涨行情还是参考意义较小，更多的时间还是要在正常行情下操作，想学学牛市收益的锚点[/quote]<br/>你先别管跑赢大盘多少个点 你先保证做对的操作  做到主线 做到正确的方向<br/>当你每一次上涨都能在对的方向  那最后的却比就是挣多和挣少而已了<br/><br/>绝大部分挣钱的例子都一样  [color=red]与其在错误的方向上狂奔，不如在对的路口稍作停留 等风来[/color]<br/><br/>然后就是控制回撤了。[color=red]上涨过程中很多时候的卖飞，本来就是半途而废里的圆满，而做错方向的出清，都是生活里最温柔的止损[/color]。<br/>当把这两个事情做对了  你的收益肯定比指数高", "lou": 2423, "content_length": 351, "reply_to": 867220017, "14": {"17": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778139382}, {"pid": 867293249, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 85, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 08:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "。。。错在哪啊。。老美也不过是正常回调而已<br/>大A你不追高映射和那种涨高的<br/>拿着什么AI软 航天 机器人 低位国产替代和国算 甚至矿产等等这些能有什么错啊<br/>那些高的反正都是每天再出利润 现在浮盈至少都是150%以上的  到底错在哪？<br/>你们不会真的去追高吧？", "lou": 2424, "content_length": 225, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778200121}, {"pid": 867295216, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 53, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 08:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867294077,45974302,4753]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43296537]夕阳余晖啊[/uid] (2026-05-08 08:37):[/b]<br/><br/>回调不是拿好筹码的机会吗[/quote]<br/>对啊<br/>站在光锂多开芯[s:ac:心]", "lou": 2425, "content_length": 21, "reply_to": 867294077, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778201278}, {"pid": 867295739, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 08:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867295569,45974302,4754]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67152095]xiaoh1992[/uid] (2026-05-08 08:51):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大你少了个存，他值得你看一眼[s:a2:doge][/quote]<br/>存储不就是芯那边的。", "lou": 2426, "content_length": 25, "reply_to": 867295569, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778201580}, {"pid": 867296980, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 09:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867296281,45974302,4754]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61395264]村上吹树[/uid] (2026-05-08 08:57):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，你的光是什么光…光…光纤？[/quote]<br/>。。。PCB CPO 光纤 还有那些光上游材料等的统称<br/>我这几个细分主要做PCB材料方向啊。。我很少做CPO的", "lou": 2427, "content_length": 95, "reply_to": 867296281, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778202192}, {"pid": 867297631, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 09:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867297466,45974302,4755]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67177520]Amam2haruna[/uid] (2026-05-08 09:07):[/b]<br/><br/>那又可以做老情人鼎泰高科了吗 鼎泰高科现在还能做吗 还是位置已经有点太高不好做了[/quote]<br/>我不做那个了啊  我在打造另外一个鼎泰高科", "lou": 2428, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 867297466, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778202512}, {"pid": 867310799, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 68, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 10:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "机器人应该是一波流 我说我自己的判断。", "lou": 2429, "content_length": 36, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778207841}, {"pid": 867311390, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 10:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867311034,45974302,4768]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39235785]Doh丶[/uid] (2026-05-08 10:38):[/b]<br/><br/>还需要更多业绩表现吗狼大[/quote]<br/>这波是商航补涨  调整后真正开始走业绩 <br/>不过现在先吃第一波 不急 等他结束 只是不要横跳了 没必要  一波流 一起上来的。", "lou": 2430, "content_length": 107, "reply_to": 867311034, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778208046}, {"pid": 867311744, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 26, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 10:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867311603,45974302,4769]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1638060]三少爷的箭[/uid] (2026-05-08 10:42):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大说的JJR已经兑现，风偏低的没必要去追高，还有游戏，AI软都没怎么涨，这么多板块可以做。[/quote]<br/>我什么时候说过机器人已经兑现？", "lou": 2431, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 867311603, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778208178}, {"pid": 867320621, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 11:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "20W的锂矿附近 鬼故事会很多<br/>我觉得不适合正常人玩", "lou": 2432, "content_length": 45, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778211451}, {"pid": 867325778, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 54, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 12:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "半导体已经有顶分型的迹象<br/>如果破位我就撤大部分了  <br/>我目前其实大部分都切换到了我的低位方向里，上面那些高位PCB 半导体都是只有被动止盈位了<br/>我还是想说一下  目前好歹是个关键压力位 大家都不是那块了，券商也没动 ，不适合自己去做突破强上加强的<br/>反而这几天我的低位方向哪个没起来  哪怕你选到没涨的他不是也没跌么。", "lou": 2433, "content_length": 287, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778213647}, {"pid": 867328083, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 77, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 12:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这波半导体材料方向确实速度太快了  我目前4个票基本剩底<br/>收益鼎龙50% 新阳25% LAW50% 格林达翻倍还多一点<br/>整个电子化学品板块从我说半导体设备切半导体材料的时候开始算起涨了快40%。<br/>是整个板块 <br/>所以我认为这波半导体强上加强去带过指数的可能性不大<br/>反而是一线光的方向 已经盘整一段时间，如果下次冲击4200可能他们会配合白线过去 不过还是那句话 二线光的幅度和舒适度都比一线光要强太多。<br/><br/>当然这里都是短线思维，长线或趋势波段这里都是接近减仓点而不是加仓点 也不是调仓点。<br/><br/>目的简单 就是保证更多的盈利能带走 而不是还给这个市场。", "lou": 2434, "content_length": 484, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778214801}, {"pid": 867329201, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 12:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867328649,45974302,4782]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67171786]无比辉煌[/uid] (2026-05-08 12:38):[/b]<br/><br/>图哥天天军训law，我还以为狼大不在hh[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202605/08/jmQ2x-9scvKfToS8m-6j.jpg[/img]<br/>你猜我什么时候做的", "lou": 2435, "content_length": 59, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202605/08/jmQ2x-9scvKfToS8m-6j.jpg", "size": 16, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202605/08", "name": "jmQ2x-9scvKfToS8m-6j.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "24"}], "reply_to": 867328649, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778215415}, {"pid": 867330897, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 12:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867330620,45974302,4783]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64289495]生鱼片是死鱼片wk[/uid] (2026-05-08 12:56):[/b]<br/><br/>设备这边我还是打算等什么时候波长或者茂莱来个20cm再减吧[s:a2:有何贵干][/quote]<br/>茂来现在是光 至少这一段是", "lou": 2436, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 867330620, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778216352}, {"pid": 867334143, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 13:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867333855,45974302,4785]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66985869]从痴有爱[/uid] (2026-05-08 13:28):[/b]<br/><br/>光迅真猛啊，国产的光居然能这么涨。[/quote]<br/>二线光补涨 我刚刚不是说了", "lou": 2437, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 867333855, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778218248}, {"pid": 867334764, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 46, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 13:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "商航这波都是提前预告给你们了  你们看看前面跌的那几天我的判断 <br/>我说能板块过新高就能过", "lou": 2438, "content_length": 80, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778218591}, {"pid": 867335670, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-05-08 13:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=867335310,45974302,4786]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=2395594]枫叶那个落尘`[/uid] (2026-05-08 13:41):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大现在,有点不知所措了... 是继续保持仓位,,还是适当止盈,还会有那一波C杀吗?  商航周日开始到中旬最关键的一波前.. 应该还有热度吧[/quote]<br/>只要过高点  C就不存在了啊  你不要学那种死技术派<br/>埋伏的就是那些人<br/>技术是之后的 是死的  <br/>我都是预判可能会出的方向 然后根据市场做应对。", "lou": 2439, "content_length": 126, "reply_to": 867335310, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1778219053}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155491, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109336, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "米璐璐6666LLL", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109357, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17":